Visibility

State Variables 

Public - Accessible inside and outside the smart contract and also inheritable

Internal - Accessible inside the smart contract and inheritable

Private -  Only accessible inside the smart contract

Functions 

Public - Can be called outside the smart contract and be called by another function within the contract

Private -  Cannot be called outside the smart contract but can be called by another function within the contract

External - Can only be called outside the smart contract

Internal - Can only be called inside the smart contract by another function
 


